Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23v\blur0.3\pos(213.928,323.39)}When you are watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(587.096,341.559)}please have the room\Nbrightly lit and be\Ncareful not to get too\Nclose to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:08.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:10.65,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(539.237,126)}CHARGE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.32,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(537,473)}CRO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:11.99,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(537,473)}MAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.28,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(537,473)}TIE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:18.83,Cromartie Title,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs52\c&H111111&\3c&H111111&\pos(354,380)}Charge!! Cromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.01,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.01,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.74,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.74,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:03.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.29,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.29,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:29.98,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord1\blur1\c&H4040E7&v\pos(106,400)}First
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.65,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(720,0)}Cromartie Municipal High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:36.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}I have been able to get enrolled\Nin Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I hope to get used to the school\Nas quickly as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and lead a healthy academic life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:43.24,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(300,0)\pos(358,385)}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I am surrounded by people\Nof unfamiliar demeanor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and I am at somewhat of a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.21,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial Black\fs22\bord20\c&H161616&\3c&HF1F1F1&\pos(166.538,206)\clip(113,170,221,224)}Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I dropped my pencil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems some of the people\Nare surprisingly nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He ate the pencil!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Cromartie High's delinquents\N certainly aren't famous for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is just not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,H-He ate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Truly, this is not your\N ordinary school of delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I feel as though this isn't really\Nan issue of being bad or delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why have I ended up in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.59,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9E9E9&\fnEraser\bord0\shad0\frz2.614\fs30\pos(252.639,46)}Today's Theme
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.59,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9E9E9&\fnEraser\bord0\shad0\pos(521.139,132)\fs32}"I Was Once Bad"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.59,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9E9E9&\fnEraser\bord0\shad0\fs36\pos(358,475)\frz0.847} Bragging Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,430)}I ask that you read the manga to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been bad since junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.26,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(524.538,389)}Other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.26,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(124.62,219)}Other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:45.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They said I was totally uncontrollable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(359.133,403)}Other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:48.56,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\alpha180\pos(359.133,403)}Other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and called me "Fireball of Junior 2".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.06,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,397)}Fireball of Junior 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, you're the legendary "Fireball"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I used to be a well-known badass too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(122.354,346)}Other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I lost it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(359.133,401)}Other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}I wouldn't stop until I'd beat\Nthe other guy to a bloody pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My street name was "Hospitalizer of Junior 3".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.57,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(355.734,392)}Hospitalizer of Junior 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Hospitalizer of Junior 3"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was bad, but I've never gotten into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:17.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I look tough, so they get scared\N and don't even try to pick fights with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And the nickname I got was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Masa of Default Victories".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.26,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(450,0)\pos(358,394)}Masa of Default Victories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, are you actually good in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, like I said, I've never been\Nin a fight, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:30.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's kinda hard to say if that's impressive or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:34.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll come out and say it,\N you guys are nothing compared to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was getting into fights\N from dawn to dusk every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course, I've never lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'd sooner punch someone than talk it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm what you'd call\N an honest to goodness badass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've even won five against one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, what was your nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My nickname was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I never really had a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then you're no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who gives a damn\Nif I have a nickname or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:08.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no point if you don't have one like\N"Fireball of Junior 2" or "Monster of Junior 3"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you're like a\N "Suzuki of Junior 4" or "Satoh,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it doesn't give off the sense that you're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry, try again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.44,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,55)}Akira Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.44,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\bord0.2\c&HD0CCCD&\move(945.981,193,378.392,193,0,2480)}Nickname coming next time...When is next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When's next time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:27.07,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\blur0.5\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\fs15\frz7.744\pos(307.019,399)}Advice on\N Debuting in\N High School\N\NChapter 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:27.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fscx107.627\blur0.5\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\fs15\frz7.744\pos(299.089,385)}Advice on\N Debuting in\N High School\N\NChapter 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:27.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fscx107.627\blur0.5\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\fs14\frz7.744\pos(294.557,369)}Advice on\N Debuting in\N High School\N\NChapter 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:27.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fscx107.627\fscy95\blur0.5\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\fs14\frz16.103\pos(291.158,388)}Advice on\N Debuting in\N High School\N\NChapter 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,two years ago in the spring of\Nmy second year in junior high,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I did something bad, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kamiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You had a nickname when you were\Nin junior high too, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like "Good-for-nothing" or "Moron".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Back in junior high, I was called "Errand Boy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.13,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\b0\pos(360.266,400)}"Errand Boy" {\b1}...someone who runs errands
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not a nickname! That's your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've never done anything bad, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:45.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, because I have been on\Nthe straight and narrow all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But even so, I have done\N something bad, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, what you call bad is probably no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like ringing doorbells and\Nrunning away or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it really was nothing big,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I do not really feel like talking\Nabout it right now, so I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.07,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs65\fnLeviBrush\b0\bord1\blur2\c&H3F9BB2&\pos(396.519,131)\frz355.087}Let's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.07,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs65\fnLeviBrush\b0\bord1\blur2\c&H3F9BB2&\pos(399.918,264)\frz352.355}Debut
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After all, those who are curious\Ncan just read the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:19.08,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\blur0.5\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\fs20\frz9\move(333.076,385,329.677,399,30,14962)\t(\fs22)}Advice on\N Debuting in\N High School\N\NChapter 1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:26.51,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\an9\blur0.7\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\fs36\frz35\t(fs44)\pos(157.475,397)}Advice on\N Debuting in\N High School\N\NChapter 1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:19.08,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(450,0)\pos(358,393)}Main Character Takashi Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}The other day, I learned of\Na revolutionary system
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}in the world of delinquents called\N"Debuting in High School".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}In this system, you can set out\Nanew as a delinquent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:19.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}even if you had led a normal life in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lesson 1: Looks are a vital part\Nof being a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Amateurs should first try\Nbleaching their hair blond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.80,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\shad0\be2\move(369.329,137,369.329,137,0,1210)\bord2\3c&H121212&\c&HF4F4F4&}20 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.22,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\shad0\be2\move(369.329,137,363.665,137,0,396)\fad(0,500)\bord2\3c&H121212&\c&HF4F4F4&}20 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:32.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If the chemical is too strong,\Nyour hair will turn white, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you still do not look fierce enough,\Ntry shaving your eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You will look even more fierce\Nif you furrow your brow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:41.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Skipping the middle part and on to Lesson 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please sever your ties with any upright people\Nyou used to be friends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please ignore them,\Neven if they try to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lesson 5 will be somewhat tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\bord3\blur0.5\c&H13172C&\3c&H7B8CA9&\fs32\pos(358,30)}Tabata      Yoshio
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:56.71,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\bord3\blur0.5\c&H13172C&\3c&H7B8CA9&\fs32\move(358,30,488.285,30,0,525)}Tabata      Yoshio
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.21,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\bord3\blur0.5\c&H13172C&\3c&H7B8CA9&\fs32\pos(488.285,30)}Tabata      Yoshio
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yoshio and Tabata are some of my best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:59.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you absolutely cannot do this,\Nplease meet with them secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Lesson 6, how to walk."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Try to relax as much as possible and walk lazily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And if anyone stares at you, glare back at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Addendum. When walking around town,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:24.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,try to walk with tough-looking friends\Nas much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:27.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,First, make lots of tough-looking friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:30.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. This might be something\Nthat would be applicable,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,not just in the world of delinquents,\Nbut out in the real world as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Once you get to this point, you are just\None step away from debuting in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now, this is the final lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please have all of the above\N completed before starting school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, go buy me some sticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lick!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.43,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad1\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\an8\fs46\blur0.5\pos(358,10)\c&H6E6E92&\bord0}Fight Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.43,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\an8\fs45\blur1\c&H7EA5EF&\bord0\pos(358,13)}Fight Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's get around to deciding who's\Nthe strongest in our class soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:57.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To start with, I've picked up a couple guys\Nbased on their history of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:06.90,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fs31\b0\pos(152.943,375)}Main character
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:06.90,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fs31\b0\pos(152.943,456)}Takashi Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,475)}Please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,475)}Why have I been nominated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,475)}You damn idiot! That's what I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,475)}Step back now, or I'll fudging kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who nominated Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! Hayashida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've been living in a world of badasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:17.45,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(400,0)\pos(358,390)}Shinjiro Hayashida
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so you don't feel scared
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}even when you see a good fighter\Nor someone who looks tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:22.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In fact, you start to feel impressed\N by normal guys like Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Aren't you pushing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:29.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,let's say there's one rabbit\Nliving happily in a pride of lions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:32.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that rabbit's one hell of a rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I get it! That IS one hell of a rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I want to see the devil that's in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I haven't the slightest what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:45.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, how are we going to decide\Nwho the strongest guy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be through fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You got that right! It's gotta be a fist fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And after a heated argument\N that went on for several hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they decided that the strongest guy would be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"the most fired up guy with the strongest\Nand most persevering back,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:00.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and that they would settle this with a contest\Nthat would fulfill these conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:04.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I hear Year 1 Class 2 is having a contest\Nto see who's the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you guys determined\Nwho's strongest yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:14.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:23.35,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,392)}Main Character Takashi Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I don't feel satisfied with the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:29.40,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArnold 2.1\fs26\blur2\bord2.5\c&H419DE3&\t(\fs31)\frz8.169\move(423.709,322,436.171,337,0,5987)}Rock You
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:28.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As the days went by, Kamiyama's thoughts about reorganizing this school strengthened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:35.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}However, as if to mock Kamiyama,\Nthe school was to follow the way of ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:35.36,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(450,0)\pos(358,392)}Shinjiro Hayashida
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:41.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama, if you could defeat HIM,\Nthis school might change too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:46.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's a real bastard in Year 1 Class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As long as he's around,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,this place will be like the Olympics\Nfor badasses every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I'll at least try meeting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Without knowing his name,\N I won't be able to see him even if I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When you get there, you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When I get there, I'll know?\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:15.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Year 1 Class 3. This is it. HE's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it! It's this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But is he really a high school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or rather, does he understand Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:35.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I am Kamiyama\Nof Year 1 Class 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but what is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the end, I didn't find out anything\Nfrom meeting with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. What a formidable guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is he really a student here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:52.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I thought of a name for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you think of Freddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:09:59.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnLauren C. Brown\fs22\b0\c&H1B1514&\2c&H1B1514&\bord0.1\blur0.7\frz342\pos(266.234,87)}Freddie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.33,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H1CD3C4&\bord0.5\blur0.8\fs50\frz10\t(\fs56)\fnJasmineUPC\move(532.468,245,553.994,245,0,3237)}Welcome \Nto the Jungle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.33,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\blur0.8\fs50\frz10\t(\fs55)\fnJasmineUPC\c&H116259&\move(534.734,247,556.259,247,0,3237)}Welcome \Nto the Jungle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Monsters dwell in Cromartie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:17.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama, there's this other\Nincredible guy in another class!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.67,0:10:17.01,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(500,0)\pos(358,190)\fnSuper Retro M54\fs23\i1\bord5\be15\c&H5CA80A&\3c&HFAFFF3&\shad0}Future Century Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:17.01,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(500,0)\pos(358,190)\fnSuper Retro M54\fs23\i1\bord12\be35\c&H5CA80A&\3c&HB1FEA0&\shad0}Future Century Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've seen enough.\N First Freddie, and then Gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All sorts of things show up at this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so nothing can surprise me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, he's incredible!\NI've never seen a badass like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've said the same thing each time,\Nyou know that, Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's trouble, Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? What kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What a sober voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:42.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it appears there will be another episode of the\Nanime; "Sakigake!! Cromartie High School"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,next time, with complete\N disregard for public opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:44.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial Black\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(539.266,391)}See you again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Oh, Hayashida. You don't need to\N show me any more "incredible" guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(113.291,470)}We'll meet again!
